item.title: SoftLayer_User_Employee_Department
item.description: SoftLayer_User_Employee_Department Datatype Description SoftLayer_User_Employee_Department models a department within SoftLayer’s internal employee hierarchy. Common departments include Support, Sales, Accounting, Development, Systems, and Networking. Local name The name of one of SoftLayer's employee departments. Type: string
